    ---**List of force types (p1)**:\
    ---public enum ForceType\
    ---{\
    ---    MinForce = 0,\
    ---    MaxForceRot = 1,\
    ---    MinForce2 = 2,\
    ---    MaxForceRot2 = 3,\
    ---    ForceNoRot = 4,\
